metadata.name: Rebecca Rose
metadata.description: Rebecca Rose is an award winning collage artist pushing boundaries with the medium through collaged sculpts and holograms across multiple NFT chains. Her 20+ year body of analog, sculptural, and digital collage has received multiple major artist grants co-sponsored by The Robert Rauschenberg Foundation, The Andy Warhol Foundation, The Joan Mitchell Foundation, The Willem de Kooning Foundation, The Andrew Mellon Foundation, The Ford Foundation, & Bloomberg Philanthropic.
